@4295 = ~Svlast's Torment
Having survived the revenant's assault with our assistance, poor and wretched Svlast has begged us to complete its task... The day is dark within these ruins, and I fear it's growing ever darker.~
@4296 = ~Svlast's Torment
Having survived the revenant's assault with our assistance, poor and wretched Svlast has begged us to complete its task... I flatly refused. He will have to atone for his crimes.~
@4297 = ~Svlast's Torment
Having survived the revenant's assault with our assistance, poor and wretched Svlast has begged us to complete its task... You'd think he would show some gratitude!~
@4298 = ~Svlast's Torment
Having survived the revenant's assault with our assistance, poor and wretched Svlast has begged us to complete its task... Who am I to refuse?~
